{"word":"ἐνοικέω","slug":"ἐνοικέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνοικέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to dwell in</i> a place, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>ἐν τόπῳ</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>[Θυρέαν] ἔδοσαν ἐνοικεῖν</el> <i>gave</i> it them <i>to dwell in</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> loci, <i>to inhabit</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>οἱ ἐνοικοῦντες</el> <i>the inhabitants</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}